songs.title: I Want U
songs.lyrics:
[Produced by David Mordeci]

[Verse 1]
I got missed calls, missed calls
From my old hoes, old hoes
I don't need her at all, at all
Hit it on the low low, low low
I need to stop drinking, drinking
Don't know what I was thinking, thinking
Don't know why she tripping, tripping
This is why I'm sipping, sipping
Cut that bullshit
Get to the real shit
Get to the real shit
I hit the kill switch
I hit it real quick
I hit it real quick
Come on my own now
I cannot slow down
I cannot slow down
I'm on my own shit
I'm on my own shit
Still on my own shit
All this shit's so different now
Yeah you still don't listen now
I can't trust these bitches right now
Chilling with all of my niggas right now

[Hook]
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you

[Verse 2]
I've been gone for so long, so long
I had to keep it low key, low key
All my hoes on roll call, roll call
And they don't even know me, know me
I'mma quit these drugs though, I mean it
I say that shit like every other weekend
She open up, I try to get between it
She sent that text but I ain't ever read it
I had to lie, I said I didn't receive it
She know I lie and no she ain't believe it
It's all good on the West side
She on my left side, that's my best side

[Hook]
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
I don't need you but I want you
